{"id":149737,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/下任美国驻华大使指责中国操控市场/","date":"2011-05-04T09:30:23Z","modified":"2012-02-17T01:31:10Z","title":"下任美国驻华大使指责中国操控市场","content":"<div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">华盛顿</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据路透社报道，预定担任下届驻华大使的美国现任商务部长骆家辉（</span><span>Gary Locke</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）抨击中国对外国企业采取歧视政策。在周三（</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）公布的一份演讲稿中，骆家辉指出，许多美国企业被排斥在整个经济领域之外。他批评说，除此之外，如果美国企业要想和中国做生意，常常不得不提供商业机密。他指出，这种商机的不平衡对进一步改善美中双边经贸关系而言是一个重大障碍。骆家辉的此番批评是在本年度美中战略与经济峰会召开前一周作出的。现任美国驻华大使洪博培（</span><span>Jon Huntsman</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）上月底离开北京。他计划明年竞选总统。奥巴马总统提名骆家辉接替担任驻华大使。该提名尚需国会参议院认可。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15047482%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%BB%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E9%A9%BB%E5%8D%8E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E6%8C%87%E8%B4%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%93%8D%E6%8E%A7%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9426,15592]}